CC  Puruvate can be fermented to 2,3-butanediol. It is first converted to alpha-acetolactate by alpha-acetolactate synthase, then decarboxylated to acetoin by this enzyme. Acetoin can be reduced in some species to 2,3-butanediol by acetoin reductase.
